                " and 12.0 MeV, respectively.",
                "In view of this, the contribution from the tail region",
                " to the 232-Th(n,g) reaction has been estimated using",
                " the ENDF/B-VII, JENDL-4.0 and JEFF-3.1 by folding the",
                " cross-sections with neutron flux distributions coded",
                " under INC-SPECT.",
                "The contributions 232-Th(n,g) to the reaction from the",
                " above evaluation at Ep = 5.6 MeV are 5.34, 5.57 and",
                " 5.03 mb from ENDF/B-VII, JENDL-4.0 and JEFF-3.1",
                " respectively.",
                "Similarly at Ep = 12 MeV, 232-Th(n,g) the reaction",
                " cross-sections from the above evaluation are 0.798",
                " and 0.876mb from ENDF/B-VII and JENDL-4.0.",
                "The actual value of the 232-Th(n, g) reaction cross-",
                " section due to the neutrons from the main peak of the",
                " n0 and n1 groups of the neutron spectrum is obtained",
                " after subtracting the average cross-section due to",
                " neutrons from the tail region from the before-",
                " mentioned experimental data."
              ]
            }
